lastfm.summary: "Way Down We Go" is a song by Icelandic rock band Kaleo, released as the second single for their first studio album A/B by Elektra Records and Atlantic Records. Commercial performance "Way Down We Go" peaked at No. 1 on Billboard's Alternative Songs and Rock Airplay charts. Live performances A live performance of the song was recorded in the magma chamber of the dormant Icelandic volcano Thrihnukagigur. Appearances in other media The song was used in the movie Collateral Beauty Read more on Last.fm.
lastfm.title: Way Down We Go
